				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document}-decay patterns and transition probabilities. In particular, the phase of the energy staggering has been suggested to be a measure of the degree of stiffness or softness of the γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
