Some very interesting outstanding questions are, what are the precise energies of the isomeric states and the heights of the inner and outer barriers? What is the nature of the decay processes? What is the branching ratio between γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
