				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document} decays in these nuclei [309].

A renewed experimental effort on study of γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
