				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$^{238}$$\end{document}U).

A Compton-suppressed, high-resolution γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
