				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document}-ray spectrometer, made of 26 HeGe detectors (named GEANIE, i.e., GErmanium Array for Neutron Induced Excitations) [371], is also installed at the white high-energy neutron facility at facility of the Los Alamos Neutron Science Center (LANSCE) [352].Fig. 47
