				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\gamma $$\end{document} beams of the ELI-NP facility come online, photofission as a production mechanism for prompt decay studies will become a reality along with new opportunities to study fission reaction mechanism induced by high-energy photons [402].
